entries.femaleVariant: Come on. Don't like leaving the door open.
[Hand over databank] Got it right here.
Here. Don't worry, it's completely intact.
You wouldn't happen to've seen what's inside, would you?
Of course not.
Yes, I did.
And ruin my cred? For what, a few bytes of data?
Funny you should say that, 'cause not long ago the databank's GPS sig suddenly went online.
It couldn't have been me.
All right, you got me.
Beats me. Who knows, maybe the scavs managed to take a little peek before I came along.
Here. You can go now.
All right, you got me. I looked inside... I know everything.
That's what I thought. So, what's your next move?
I wanna congratulate you.
Blackmail you, of course.
Nothing.
To congratulate you, of course. Anyone who hacks Night Corp's earned my respect.
entries.maleVariant: To congratulate you, of course. Anyone who hacks Night Corp has earned my respect.

entries.femaleVariant: Oh, well I... um... thank you. You know, if they end up going through with it, then--
What daemons did you use?
Conditioning people's minds... that's just evil.
Night Corp's secured up the ass. Can't just upload the usual Blackout and Fireshaft.
You've been a big help. Here. I threw in a little extra – for a fellow runner.
Thanks. Be seein' ya.
Usin' AGI to condition workers' minds... Hm, that's some supervillain shit right there.
entries.maleVariant: Usin' AGI to condition workers' minds... Huh, that's some supervillain shit right there.

entries.femaleVariant: Here. What we agreed on... plus a little extra. People like us need to stick together, right?
Thanks. And good luck.
You've got a pretty nice place... for a netrunner. Wonder how someone like you could afford all this...
Here! This much.
Nothing. I don't care what you do in your spare time. After all – it's a free country, am I right?
entries.maleVariant: Nothin'. I don't care what you do in your spare time. After all – it's a free country, right?

entries.femaleVariant: Anyway, I'll take your indifference as a sign of good faith. Here. You can go now.
Thanks. Be seein' ya.
I'm a professional. I have a reputation to uphold.
Hm. Good. Then here you go. For your professionalism.
[Knock]
Sandra? It's me, V. Got your databank.
entries.maleVariant: Sandra? It's me, V. I got your databank.

entries.femaleVariant: Are you alone? Did anyone follow you?
What does it look like?
Sandra! You in there?
Still worried about the scavs? My, uh... friend told me your memory'd be scraped clean.
entries.maleVariant: Still worried about the scavs? My, um... friend told me your memory'd be scraped clean.

entries.femaleVariant: The scavengers? No, I'm worried about... Umm... No, no, it doesn't matter.
You bring the databank?
The Net'll become even more dangerous. You were worried they'd find out about you.
Exactly.
Thanks. Be seein' ya.
Eventually, it'll let them control anyone they want. That's what scares me the most.
Glad to see there're runners who're findin' old school dirt like this. I just hope it gets put to good use.
Oh, it will. Don't you worry about that.
Heh, that's what they want you to think. You haven't seen what I've seen.
Would be a shame if Night Corp got an anonymous tip that somebody'd broken into their database...
Huh, doesn't surprise me – someone like you. You're no better than a scavenger.
Please, don't exaggerate. Now then, how much is my silence worth to you?
Which can only mean one thing – someone booted it up and used it.
Mhm. The scavs. Sure...
Now wait a sec, we agreed on more!
Oh, really? I guess the scavs must've taken a peek at my bank account before you got here.
We're done. Now leave.
You must've whipped up some angry daemons. You zip 'em up in an Imp?
Yeah, Leviathan. Even Cerberus isn't enough if you wanna punch through that kind of corpo ICE.
Usin' AGI to condition workers' minds... Hm, that's some supervillain shit right there.
entries.maleVariant: Usin' AGI to condition workers' minds... Huh, that's some supervillain shit right there.

entries.femaleVariant: Not just workers – anyone. That's the scariest part.
What are you worried about?
If it's not the scavs you're worried about, then who?
Look, I didn't pay you to come here and ask me personal questions.
Hey, you mentioned it. 'Sides, I saved your life. That isn't worth anything?
It was worth whatever you got paid. Don't pretend I wasn't just another small-time job for you.
Now, did you bring the databank?
When someone tells me not to worry, it usually means they're hiding something.
I threw in a little extra for minding your own data.
It's good to be reminded I'm not in this fight alone.
How much for keeping my mouth shut?
I was just kidding.
Relax, I was just pullin' your leg. I'm not that big of a cunt.
entries.maleVariant: Relax, I was just pullin' your leg. I'm not that big of a dick.

entries.femaleVariant: Think that's funny, do you?
Take your eddies and... and get out.
Out! Now!
You have good taste.
Nice place you got here. Tasteful.
Thanks.
Cozy place.
Nice digs.
[Knock] Sandra?
